  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════ SEO STRATEGY ══════════ -->
<div class="page">
  <p class="section-eyebrow">Step 3 — Africa Tourism SEO Strategy</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">How We Get Africa Leads<br>Through Google</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">SEO means making your website appear when someone types relevant searches into Google. Here is the step-by-step plan for Africa tourism.</p>

